---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from "../../components/LeadForm.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../components/RelatedServices.astro';
import mntPhoto from '../../assets/images/medical-nutrition-education.jpg';

const seo = {
  title: 'Medical Nutrition Therapy | KM Wellness Center | El Paso, TX',
  description:
    'Optimize your health with personalized medical nutrition therapy at KM Wellness Center. Discover tailored plans for lasting wellness.',
};
---
<BaseLayout {...seo}>
  <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Services', href: '/services/' }, { name: 'Medical Nutrition Therapy', href: '/services/medical-nutrition/' }]} />
  <h1>Medical Nutrition Therapy: A Personalized Approach to Health</h1>

  <p>
    At KM Wellness Center, we work to improve health by using medical nutrition therapy (MNT) as a
    therapeutic tool. This personalized approach helps address various health conditions like
    diabetes, cardiovascular disease, and obesity. MNT goes beyond typical dietary advice, focusing on
    how tailored nutrition plans can address specific medical needs.
  </p>

  <Image
    class="feature-photo"
    src={mntPhoto}
    alt="Registered dietitian leading a medical nutrition therapy session at KM Wellness Center in El Paso"
    widths={[420, 640, 860]}
    sizes="(min-width: 900px) 860px, 100vw"
    format="webp"
    quality={75}
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
  />

  <section>
    <h2>What Is Medical Nutrition Therapy?</h2>
    <p>
      Medical Nutrition Therapy involves a comprehensive nutritional assessment performed by a
      registered dietitian or nutrition professional. The goal is to understand a patient's current
      dietary habits, health status, and medical history to create a customized nutrition plan. By
      using evidence-based nutrition science, MNT is effective in managing chronic diseases and
      improving overall wellness.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>The Benefits of Nutrition Therapy</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Improved Disease Management:</strong> Tailored meal plans help regulate blood sugar, cholesterol, and other important markers for conditions like diabetes, high blood pressure, and kidney disease.</li>
      <li><strong>Personalized Care:</strong> Individualized diet plans address each patient's unique health challenges.</li>
      <li><strong>Preventative Care:</strong> MNT can help prevent future health issues by promoting balanced nutrition and a healthy lifestyle.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Nutritional Diagnosis and Assessment</h2>
    <p>
      A critical part of MNT is performing a nutritional diagnosis to identify underlying issues
      related to poor diet. The nutritionist evaluates weight history, food intake, physical activity,
      and medical conditions, and reviews lab results, medications, and a complete health profile to
      determine the best dietary intervention.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Medical Nutrition Therapy for Weight Loss</h2>
    <p>
      Obesity is often linked to other health conditions such as Type 2 diabetes, heart disease, and
      metabolic syndrome. Our team provides metabolic assessments that help patients understand how
      their bodies process food and burn energy, emphasizing sustainable changes rather than crash
      diets.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Why Choose KM Wellness Center for Nutrition Therapy?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Comprehensive nutritional assessments</li>
      <li>Personalized nutrition plans</li>
      <li>Continuous monitoring and support</li>
      <li>Evidence-based care</li>
    </ul>
    <p><a href="/contact-us/">Make an appointment</a></p>
  </section>

  <RelatedServices current="/services/medical-nutrition/" />

  <LeadForm source="medical-nutrition" service="Medical Nutrition Therapy" />
</BaseLayout>
